  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary objective of this study is to evaluate the safety and efficacy of clobetasol
      propionate spray versus vehicle spray for the management of moderate to severe plaque
      psoriasis of the scalp.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
